name: PolygonPunks
description: PolygonPunks are the 1st Punk NFTs on the Polygon blockchain. Each of the PolygonPunks has attributes that make them unique according to a defined rarity system. The entire collection of 10,000 Punks were officially minted out on August 3rd, 2021, solidifying their history as the 1st Punks on Polygon.
